WEBVTT

01:37.789 --> 01:40.710
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.229 --> 01:43.670
[Episode 14]

01:44.509 --> 01:45.200
Too much blood

01:45.200 --> 01:46.789
has been shed over these jade tablets.

01:46.789 --> 01:47.650
It really is...

01:48.920 --> 01:49.840
It really is...

01:50.590 --> 01:52.250
The outcome is hard to change.

01:52.759 --> 01:54.350
Hopefully, one day in the future,

01:54.350 --> 01:56.210
there will be a perfect solution.

01:57.070 --> 01:58.509
I never thought about outcomes

01:58.509 --> 01:59.310
or the future.

01:59.560 --> 02:00.760
I just kept thinking—

02:00.760 --> 02:02.870
I've never seen anyone
achieve immortality,

02:02.870 --> 02:04.560
but I have seen a lot of dead people.

02:04.560 --> 02:06.820
That definitely can't be anything good.

02:07.280 --> 02:07.790
True.

02:10.280 --> 02:11.400
But then again,

02:11.590 --> 02:12.240
Mr. Lu,

02:12.590 --> 02:14.030
can Divine Doctor Su really make

02:14.030 --> 02:15.000
the Immortality Pills?

02:15.000 --> 02:15.840
And can the pills

02:15.840 --> 02:17.440
truly make people immortal?

02:18.590 --> 02:20.310
Didn't you say you don't want them?

02:20.310 --> 02:21.710
Well, I'm still curious.

02:22.400 --> 02:23.130
I don't know.

02:23.800 --> 02:24.910
But isn't Divine Doctor Su

02:24.910 --> 02:25.960
your disciple?

02:26.310 --> 02:27.640
He didn't even tell you?

02:28.079 --> 02:29.630
Go ask him yourself
if you don't believe me.

02:29.630 --> 02:30.760
He wouldn't tell me.

02:31.680 --> 02:33.240
There are six jade tablets in total.

02:33.240 --> 02:33.840
One for me,

02:33.870 --> 02:34.600
one for Li Si,

02:34.680 --> 02:35.480
one for Cai En,

02:35.710 --> 02:37.110
and four for Lin Muhan...

02:38.360 --> 02:39.430
Did you take one fewer,

02:39.430 --> 02:39.960
Mr. Lu?

02:40.590 --> 02:41.470
Go back and check for yourself

02:41.470 --> 02:42.400
if you don't believe me.

02:42.400 --> 02:44.280
How am I supposed to go back and check
at this point?

02:44.280 --> 02:45.800
But then again,

02:46.000 --> 02:46.750
does immortality

02:46.750 --> 02:48.030
mean truly undying and indestructible,

02:48.030 --> 02:49.840
or just extending one's lifespan?

02:49.840 --> 02:51.400
Can it make humans like the War Demons,

02:51.400 --> 02:53.000
living for thousands of years?

02:53.000 --> 02:54.400
Then what would the world even look like

02:54.400 --> 02:55.860
after thousands of years?

03:03.120 --> 03:03.960
Divine Doctor Su,

03:03.960 --> 03:05.090
why are you all here?

03:10.280 --> 03:10.800
Master,

03:11.680 --> 03:12.560
it's time.

03:18.060 --> 03:20.890
[Jiujue Cave]

03:47.680 --> 03:49.280
Prepare to light the incense

03:49.520 --> 03:50.450
to start timing.

03:50.960 --> 03:51.620
-Yes.
-Yes.

04:16.800 --> 04:18.399
It'll take at least six hours

04:19.390 --> 04:22.190
for the Dragon Burning Sand
to dissolve his bones.

04:22.560 --> 04:25.420
To maintain the medicinal potency
the entire time,

04:25.430 --> 04:27.960
we must continuously
add fresh ingredients.

04:28.070 --> 04:28.870
Xu Changshou,

04:29.510 --> 04:31.310
oversee the sand pool yourself.

04:31.480 --> 04:33.240
If the potency weakens even slightly,

04:33.240 --> 04:34.720
add more medicine immediately.

04:34.720 --> 04:35.390
No delays.

04:36.190 --> 04:36.720
Yes.

04:39.480 --> 04:40.140
Fang Liang,

04:40.600 --> 04:41.870
is the Long Jade ready?

04:42.159 --> 04:43.560
It's long been prepared.

04:43.920 --> 04:44.750
The Long Jade

04:45.630 --> 04:47.630
is similar in hardness to his bones.

04:48.000 --> 04:48.870
You stay here.

04:50.120 --> 04:51.560
If the Long Jade in the sand pool

04:51.560 --> 04:53.120
stops melting,

04:54.040 --> 04:55.190
or if anything unusual happens,

04:55.190 --> 04:56.520
inform me immediately.

04:56.630 --> 04:57.600
Yes, Master.

05:02.310 --> 05:04.240
The stone marrow in War Demon bones

05:05.480 --> 05:07.080
is best at suppressing pain.

05:07.630 --> 05:10.630
Now that all the bones in his body
have been shattered,

05:11.190 --> 05:12.990
the stone marrow will dissolve,

05:13.630 --> 05:15.310
and he will start to feel the pain.

05:15.310 --> 05:17.160
The pain will keep building.

05:17.830 --> 05:19.960
Watch carefully for the right moment,

05:20.070 --> 05:22.000
then gag him

05:22.310 --> 05:24.170
so he doesn't bite off his tongue.

05:24.830 --> 05:25.360
Yes.

05:33.800 --> 05:34.830
Please don't worry, Master.

05:34.830 --> 05:35.750
I've already prepared ample supplies

05:35.750 --> 05:37.630
of Anesthesia Brew and clematis roots—

05:37.630 --> 05:39.270
ready to relieve the Grandmaster's pain
at any moment.

05:39.270 --> 05:41.200
Not nearly enough. Not even close!

05:41.560 --> 05:44.090
This is the pain
of having every bone crushed.

05:44.120 --> 05:45.780
Have you ever experienced it?

05:46.000 --> 05:47.000
Compared to this,

05:47.510 --> 05:49.870
poison that burns through the intestines,
flesh flayed from bone,

05:49.870 --> 05:51.190
teeth pulled, and tendons stripped

05:51.190 --> 05:52.750
is nothing more than a scratch—

05:52.750 --> 05:54.280
not even worth mentioning!

05:54.750 --> 05:56.210
He's lived his entire life

05:56.680 --> 05:58.940
never having known what pain feels like.

05:59.510 --> 06:02.240
Experiencing such agony
for the very first time,

06:02.390 --> 06:04.650
he definitely won't be able to endure it.

06:12.120 --> 06:13.070
The Grandmaster's bones

06:13.070 --> 06:14.310
have completely dissolved.

06:14.310 --> 06:15.190
We've used a leather strap

06:15.190 --> 06:16.120
to gag him

06:16.390 --> 06:17.920
to prevent him from biting off his tongue.

06:17.920 --> 06:19.830
How can he still scream?

06:22.680 --> 06:23.630
Was his head

06:24.750 --> 06:26.480
not submerged in the sand pool?

06:29.560 --> 06:30.820
Is the skull not a bone?

06:31.480 --> 06:33.409
Or does it not need to be dissolved?

06:34.290 --> 06:34.950
Got it.

07:15.000 --> 07:16.750
Lu Qianqiao, endure it.

07:17.720 --> 07:19.850
Don't think being human is any easier.

07:23.800 --> 07:24.860
Add more medicine.

07:25.120 --> 07:25.780
-Yes.
-Yes.

07:52.480 --> 07:53.120
Miss Xin,

07:53.800 --> 07:55.060
why are you still here?

07:58.720 --> 07:59.450
Are you sick?

08:00.040 --> 08:01.390
Why do you look so pale?

08:03.190 --> 08:03.920
I'm fine.

08:05.160 --> 08:06.920
Why hasn't Mr. Lu come out yet?

08:07.620 --> 08:08.750
What exactly did you

08:09.120 --> 08:10.180
bring him here for?

08:13.920 --> 08:15.180
The Grandmaster is...

08:17.360 --> 08:18.760
is receiving treatment.

08:18.920 --> 08:19.720
Rest assured.

08:19.750 --> 08:20.750
The finest physicians in Chongling Valley

08:20.750 --> 08:21.610
are all inside,

08:22.120 --> 08:23.750
and my master is personally
watching over him.

08:23.750 --> 08:25.010
Nothing will go wrong.

08:27.480 --> 08:28.480
Go back, Miss Xin.

08:28.800 --> 08:29.510
In two days,

08:29.510 --> 08:31.270
the Pill-Tasting Conference will begin.

08:31.270 --> 08:33.120
You should go back and prepare.

08:34.030 --> 08:34.549
Go back.

09:05.150 --> 09:05.790
Miss Lyu,

09:06.150 --> 09:07.480
you were looking for me?

09:12.000 --> 09:12.930
You're leaving?

09:18.010 --> 09:19.000
Dr. Zhu Yu's prescription

09:19.000 --> 09:20.530
has been working very well.

09:20.960 --> 09:22.290
I've mostly recovered.

09:22.870 --> 09:25.390
As long as I keep taking it,
I should make a full recovery.

09:25.390 --> 09:26.450
That's wonderful.

09:26.610 --> 09:27.570
So when

09:27.600 --> 09:29.060
are you planning to leave?

09:29.870 --> 09:30.510
Tomorrow.

09:31.120 --> 09:33.360
So I came to say goodbye.

09:34.240 --> 09:35.700
You're leaving tomorrow?

09:42.600 --> 09:43.320
Take it.

09:44.030 --> 09:44.600
Take it.

09:45.390 --> 09:46.910
Your medicine has cost you
far too much already.

09:46.910 --> 09:48.910
And you can keep it for emergencies.

09:49.080 --> 09:49.720
Take it.

09:57.720 --> 09:59.380
I want to see Divine Doctor Su.

09:59.390 --> 10:00.840
He and the others cured my illness.

10:00.840 --> 10:01.900
I want to thank him.

10:02.510 --> 10:03.120
Okay.

10:03.550 --> 10:04.480
I'll ask for you.

10:06.320 --> 10:06.960
Thank you.

10:08.030 --> 10:08.960
You're welcome.

10:12.000 --> 10:15.070
[Chongling Valley]

10:32.270 --> 10:33.270
Don't be nervous.

10:34.630 --> 10:35.910
You didn't sleep well?

10:36.670 --> 10:37.440
I'm fine.

10:37.550 --> 10:38.750
Don't worry about me.

10:48.510 --> 10:49.120
Miss Xin,

10:49.240 --> 10:50.270
my master has agreed.

10:50.270 --> 10:52.670
Divine Doctor Su is
waiting for you inside.

10:54.030 --> 10:54.720
Go ahead.

10:57.670 --> 10:58.400
Please go in.

11:11.750 --> 11:12.870
No need for formalities.

11:12.870 --> 11:13.720
Go on in.

11:25.120 --> 11:26.380
Don't worry, Miss Xin.

11:26.480 --> 11:27.630
The Grandmaster's condition

11:27.630 --> 11:28.890
has already improved.

11:29.120 --> 11:30.080
In a few more days,

11:30.080 --> 11:31.910
he'll be able to come out of seclusion.

11:31.910 --> 11:33.030
I was just asking.

11:34.630 --> 11:35.690
The Grandmaster is

11:35.720 --> 11:36.720
currently being sustained entirely

11:36.720 --> 11:37.910
by herbal decoctions.

11:37.910 --> 11:40.030
He hasn't been able to take liquid food
these past few days,

11:40.030 --> 11:41.840
let alone the basket full of

11:41.840 --> 11:43.600
nourishing ingredients that you brought.

11:43.600 --> 11:44.460
And that cloak—

11:44.480 --> 11:45.840
he won't be needing it either.

11:45.840 --> 11:46.720
Chongling Valley

11:46.720 --> 11:47.510
is very warm.

11:48.120 --> 11:50.180
Besides, there are robes and bedding

11:50.240 --> 11:51.300
in the Jiujue Cave.

11:51.740 --> 11:52.410
Miss Xin,

11:52.440 --> 11:54.170
you really don't need to worry.

11:55.080 --> 11:57.410
You didn't sleep well last night, did you?

11:58.600 --> 11:59.170
In a bit,

11:59.200 --> 12:00.600
I'll prescribe something calming for you

12:00.600 --> 12:01.390
to drink before bed.

12:01.390 --> 12:02.120
No need.

12:02.440 --> 12:03.640
I'll just rest early.

12:05.960 --> 12:06.360
Why...

12:07.320 --> 12:08.980
Why are you apologizing to me?

12:09.480 --> 12:10.000
What?

12:11.510 --> 12:13.040
Doesn't this mean "sorry"?

12:28.280 --> 12:29.510
What does this mean?

12:33.540 --> 12:34.730
Thank you.

12:47.750 --> 12:49.950
"Hooves thunder with mournful neighs;

12:50.030 --> 12:52.090
banners fly, and drums shake the sky.

12:52.870 --> 12:55.030
Charge forward with a sharp blade in hand;

12:55.030 --> 12:57.560
urgent military dispatches
come rushing in.

12:57.910 --> 12:59.710
This life is not mine to cherish;

13:00.030 --> 13:02.600
I'd hasten to serve my nation
in its hour of peril.

13:02.600 --> 13:04.390
Charge deep into enemy ranks;

13:04.960 --> 13:07.120
even death is a worthy price."

13:08.960 --> 13:10.120
Did you write this?

13:12.720 --> 13:14.030
Mr. Li wrote it.

13:14.670 --> 13:16.360
Could someone who writes such poetry

13:16.360 --> 13:17.270
be a bad person?

13:18.360 --> 13:20.220
Would he truly seek immortality?

13:26.750 --> 13:28.410
I want to see Divine Doctor Su.

13:28.440 --> 13:29.990
He and the others cured my illness.

13:29.990 --> 13:31.110
I want to thank him.

14:03.150 --> 14:03.910
Why?

14:04.790 --> 14:06.030
You shouldn't have come back.

14:06.030 --> 14:06.550
Tell me,

14:06.870 --> 14:07.550
why?

14:10.480 --> 14:11.140
Step aside.

14:11.720 --> 14:13.050
I don't want to hurt you.

14:13.950 --> 14:14.550
Move!

14:28.030 --> 14:29.160
Don't take her life!

15:11.000 --> 15:14.170
[Peace and Harmony]

15:25.080 --> 15:25.870
I'm sorry.

15:27.080 --> 15:27.960
I lied to you.

15:28.390 --> 15:30.190
You're not Lyu Jing's daughter.

15:30.720 --> 15:31.850
Who are you, really?

15:34.150 --> 15:34.870
Xing.

15:35.510 --> 15:36.670
That's my name.

15:38.000 --> 15:38.750
Xing...

15:39.800 --> 15:41.240
I heard that the fourth-ranked swordsman

15:41.240 --> 15:42.360
on the List of Top Martial Artists

15:42.360 --> 15:43.690
is actually two people.

15:44.720 --> 15:46.320
One uses a short sword in his left hand—

15:46.320 --> 15:47.440
their technique light, nimble,

15:47.440 --> 15:49.000
and swift as a shooting star.

15:49.000 --> 15:50.790
The other wields
a heavy sword with his right hand—

15:50.790 --> 15:52.720
striking like thunder,
overwhelming in force.

15:52.720 --> 15:53.440
Together,

15:53.630 --> 15:55.110
they possess both speed and strength—

15:55.110 --> 15:56.640
nearly flawless in combat.

15:57.150 --> 15:58.600
If I'm not mistaken,

15:59.840 --> 16:01.120
you and Li Si are

16:01.750 --> 16:03.750
the Star-and-Thunder Twin Swords.

16:06.870 --> 16:08.600
So you came to Chongling Valley

16:08.840 --> 16:10.570
for the Immortality Pills too?

16:18.390 --> 16:19.480
Who would want

16:19.800 --> 16:21.000
something like that?

16:23.390 --> 16:25.200
If not for the Immortality Pills,

16:25.200 --> 16:26.930
then it's for Divine Doctor Su.

16:28.440 --> 16:29.120
Yes.

16:32.030 --> 16:32.600
Xing,

16:33.870 --> 16:35.080
can you tell me why?

16:41.670 --> 16:42.550
Mei,

16:44.120 --> 16:45.840
how old are you?

16:56.600 --> 16:58.330
I joined the immortal sect at 12

16:58.480 --> 17:00.180
and have been cultivating for decades.

17:00.180 --> 17:01.350
By

17:01.380 --> 17:02.380
human standards,

17:02.960 --> 17:03.790
I suppose

17:04.440 --> 17:05.200
I would be

17:05.200 --> 17:07.000
a white-haired old woman by now.

17:09.000 --> 17:11.130
Then you really are quite long-lived.

17:12.680 --> 17:13.349
My mother

17:13.750 --> 17:15.480
died when I was six.

17:16.569 --> 17:18.569
There was a locust plague that year,

17:18.589 --> 17:21.069
and the harvest was
less than 20 percent of normal,

17:21.069 --> 17:23.530
yet the authorities pressed hard
for taxes.

17:23.680 --> 17:25.240
Even the last bit of grain

17:25.270 --> 17:26.400
we'd kept for winter

17:26.790 --> 17:27.829
was taken away.

17:29.270 --> 17:30.030
My mother

17:30.310 --> 17:30.970
and brother

17:31.830 --> 17:33.630
both starved to death that year.

17:35.400 --> 17:37.030
When I was 10,

17:37.350 --> 17:38.440
my father died too.

17:40.400 --> 17:41.960
The three of them together

17:43.030 --> 17:45.230
might not even have lived as long as you.

17:48.790 --> 17:51.650
The tax they levied was called
the Immortality Tax.

17:51.920 --> 17:53.510
They collected it
in spring during plowing,

17:53.510 --> 17:55.170
in autumn during the harvest,

17:55.640 --> 17:58.000
and even on holidays.

18:00.310 --> 18:02.510
The emperor's dynasty endures forever,

18:02.510 --> 18:04.550
and the immortal sects pursue
eternal life—

18:04.550 --> 18:05.720
yet only our lives

18:06.400 --> 18:07.330
become cheaper.

18:09.510 --> 18:11.710
I know Divine Doctor Su is a good person.

18:11.920 --> 18:13.070
He heals the sick

18:13.200 --> 18:14.930
and gives out medicine freely,

18:15.000 --> 18:16.130
saving many people.

18:16.750 --> 18:18.480
But as long as he's still alive,

18:19.310 --> 18:20.510
your immortal sects will keep dreaming

18:20.510 --> 18:21.680
of living forever.

18:22.510 --> 18:24.200
Then we common folks

18:25.030 --> 18:26.560
will have no way to survive.

18:28.160 --> 18:30.090
Actually, he's nearly succeeded.

18:30.240 --> 18:31.900
That's even more terrifying.

18:34.750 --> 18:35.480
Mei,

18:36.680 --> 18:37.880
you're a cultivator.

18:38.920 --> 18:40.650
You stand high up in the clouds.

18:41.030 --> 18:42.440
You probably can't understand

18:42.440 --> 18:44.640
how desperate life is for people like us

18:44.800 --> 18:46.010
at the bottom.

18:47.790 --> 18:48.790
Right now, you're

18:49.340 --> 18:51.480
different from everyone else
in the valley.

18:51.480 --> 18:53.270
There's kindness in your heart.

18:53.270 --> 18:54.470
You're still willing

18:54.920 --> 18:55.960
to reach out a hand

18:56.520 --> 18:57.720
to people like us,

18:57.750 --> 18:58.810
rotting in the mud.

19:02.590 --> 19:03.960
But I don't believe

19:04.640 --> 19:07.110
that everyone who can get their hands on
the Immortality Pills

19:07.110 --> 19:08.270
would be like you.

19:12.890 --> 19:14.350
Why are you giving me this?

19:17.750 --> 19:19.150
If the Immortality Pills

19:19.270 --> 19:21.350
must one day come into the world,

19:22.960 --> 19:23.510
I would rather

19:23.510 --> 19:24.830
they be in your hands.

19:52.270 --> 19:53.130
They're yours.

19:53.440 --> 19:54.440
I can't take them.

19:54.580 --> 19:56.240
They're useless to me anyway.

19:56.550 --> 19:57.550
Giving them to you

19:57.640 --> 19:59.700
might make you think more carefully.

20:00.270 --> 20:01.270
Think about what?

20:01.440 --> 20:02.570
About immortality.

20:02.790 --> 20:04.510
When something is beyond reach,

20:04.510 --> 20:06.750
people will pursue it
with everything they have.

20:06.750 --> 20:07.440
Only when it's firmly

20:07.440 --> 20:08.640
within your grasp

20:09.110 --> 20:10.550
will you begin to question

20:10.550 --> 20:12.810
whether it's truly a blessing or a curse.

20:13.200 --> 20:13.790
Master,

20:14.070 --> 20:15.160
a letter came from Chongling Valley.

20:15.160 --> 20:16.920
It says the Immortality Pills
are about to be completed.

20:16.920 --> 20:18.780
Master, there's hope for you now!

20:19.510 --> 20:20.440
We're not going.

20:21.640 --> 20:22.350
Why?

20:22.850 --> 20:24.440
Master, don't you want to live forever?

20:24.440 --> 20:26.100
We're just not going, anyway!

20:32.030 --> 20:32.920
Miss Xin,

20:33.310 --> 20:34.370
what are you doing?

20:34.590 --> 20:35.590
Divine Doctor Su.

20:36.000 --> 20:37.060
Please have a seat.

20:38.070 --> 20:39.160
My favorite.

20:39.510 --> 20:40.330
That's good.

20:47.160 --> 20:49.240
You're just leaving them out
on the table like this?

20:49.240 --> 20:51.570
Aren't you afraid someone will take them?

20:51.590 --> 20:53.480
Only one of these is mine.

20:54.160 --> 20:55.200
One was brought

20:55.200 --> 20:56.130
by Li Si and Xing.

20:56.550 --> 20:57.200
The rest

20:58.070 --> 20:59.470
were given to me by Mr. Lu.

21:08.240 --> 21:09.200
What's this for?

21:12.640 --> 21:14.170
I misjudged them this time.

21:14.470 --> 21:15.880
I brought Li Si and Xing into the valley

21:15.880 --> 21:17.340
and almost got you killed.

21:18.000 --> 21:20.030
Why bring that up all of a sudden?

21:20.790 --> 21:21.750
If it hadn't been them,

21:21.750 --> 21:23.480
it would've been someone else.

21:24.570 --> 21:26.000
As long as I live

21:26.110 --> 21:28.680
and the Immortality Pills
exist in the world,

21:29.000 --> 21:30.590
assassination attempts like this

21:30.590 --> 21:32.150
are inevitable.

21:33.270 --> 21:34.200
Come on.

21:38.830 --> 21:39.830
Divine Doctor Su,

21:40.070 --> 21:41.070
can you stop?

21:49.680 --> 21:50.510
Miss Xin,

21:51.240 --> 21:52.440
not everyone

21:52.720 --> 21:53.880
has a way

21:55.310 --> 21:56.240
back.

22:00.400 --> 22:01.530
You have no way back,

22:01.920 --> 22:02.680
but I do.

22:11.830 --> 22:12.830
Divine Doctor Su,

22:13.350 --> 22:14.550
I'd like to leave now.

22:16.030 --> 22:16.960
I originally came here

22:16.960 --> 22:18.270
hoping to obtain an Immortality Pill

22:18.270 --> 22:19.870
to prolong my master's life.

22:20.350 --> 22:21.240
But he

22:22.030 --> 22:23.030
didn't want that.

22:23.880 --> 22:25.480
I didn't understand before,

22:25.720 --> 22:26.440
but now,

22:27.960 --> 22:29.220
I think I do, somewhat.

22:31.630 --> 22:32.910
My master once said,

22:33.310 --> 22:34.960
"All things must come to an end—

22:34.960 --> 22:36.830
only when the sun sets
does the moon rise."

22:36.830 --> 22:38.190
Living forever

22:38.480 --> 22:39.550
in this world

22:40.790 --> 22:42.720
might not be a good thing after all.

22:44.830 --> 22:46.030
So, Divine Doctor Su,

22:46.920 --> 22:47.680
I'm leaving.

22:48.350 --> 22:50.080
I won't wait for Mr. Lu anymore.

22:50.790 --> 22:51.750
Thank you all

22:52.200 --> 22:54.330
for taking care of me during this time.

22:54.680 --> 22:56.310
When I have the chance in the future,

22:56.310 --> 22:57.110
I will thank

22:57.110 --> 22:58.440
Mr. Lu in person as well.

23:04.110 --> 23:04.910
Alright then.

23:06.200 --> 23:07.510
It's getting late.

23:09.400 --> 23:11.260
I still have matters to attend to,

23:11.920 --> 23:13.450
so I won't be seeing you off.

23:15.920 --> 23:16.920
Divine Doctor Su,

23:16.960 --> 23:18.220
these jade tablets...

23:19.880 --> 23:20.750
Miss Xin,

23:22.440 --> 23:23.900
does your master's saying

23:25.160 --> 23:26.310
have a second half?

23:28.640 --> 23:30.370
"All things must come to an end—

23:30.920 --> 23:33.030
only when the sun sets does the moon rise.

23:33.030 --> 23:34.760
As I descend the mountain path,

23:35.140 --> 23:37.140
others will still rise to climb it."

23:38.790 --> 23:40.590
"As I descend the mountain path,

23:42.880 --> 23:44.880
others will still rise to climb it."

23:46.480 --> 23:47.240
Good.

23:48.720 --> 23:49.480
Very good!

24:29.030 --> 24:29.590
Master.

24:31.750 --> 24:32.310
Master,

24:32.880 --> 24:34.080
everything is ready.

24:38.720 --> 24:39.640
Well prepared.

24:41.160 --> 24:42.090
We can start now.

25:44.250 --> 25:48.220
[Xieyun Cottage]

25:48.390 --> 25:53.070
[Suwen Hall]

25:50.240 --> 25:51.510
Where are you going?

25:52.030 --> 25:52.890
Back to my sect.

25:53.440 --> 25:54.750
Isn't today the day
that all immortal sects

25:54.750 --> 25:55.960
gather at Longevity Hall

25:55.960 --> 25:57.220
to carve up the spoils—

25:58.030 --> 25:59.830
I mean, the pills?

26:02.920 --> 26:05.070
You know how to
get out of the valley, right?

26:05.070 --> 26:05.880
When I came here,

26:05.880 --> 26:06.920
I took Zhang Dahu's boat.

26:06.920 --> 26:08.110
Good heavens!

26:08.220 --> 26:09.130
He's a scammer!

26:09.160 --> 26:10.510
Aren't you a disciple
from the immortal sect?

26:10.510 --> 26:12.170
How could you be fooled by him?

26:13.070 --> 26:13.920
Did he say

26:13.960 --> 26:15.030
he's one of us?

26:15.240 --> 26:15.830
Yeah.

26:16.070 --> 26:16.960
Yeah, my foot!

26:17.280 --> 26:18.440
He's not even a distant relative

26:18.440 --> 26:19.240
of an apprentice here.

26:19.240 --> 26:20.270
He just hangs around here,

26:20.270 --> 26:21.590
scalping queue numbers!

26:21.590 --> 26:22.960
He occasionally runs errands,

26:22.960 --> 26:23.750
delivers messages,

26:23.750 --> 26:25.150
or ferries people across

26:25.720 --> 26:26.960
to earn some extra cash.

26:26.960 --> 26:28.070
Although he doesn't charge much,

26:28.070 --> 26:29.470
he's still not reliable.

26:30.720 --> 26:31.640
No way...

26:33.920 --> 26:34.720
I'm free today.

26:34.720 --> 26:36.580
I'll escort you out of the valley.

26:36.830 --> 26:37.510
Okay then.

26:37.640 --> 26:38.310
Thank you.

26:42.240 --> 26:43.790
But speaking of which,

26:44.510 --> 26:45.710
you just reminded me.

26:46.680 --> 26:47.480
I don't think

26:47.680 --> 26:48.720
I've seen

26:48.750 --> 26:50.400
Zhang Dahu for several days now.

26:50.400 --> 26:51.270
Could he have

26:51.550 --> 26:53.080
made enough money and left?

26:53.720 --> 26:54.830
Is scalping queue numbers

26:54.830 --> 26:55.830
that profitable?

27:01.260 --> 27:02.180
How could this have happened?

27:02.180 --> 27:03.040
What happened?

27:03.040 --> 27:04.000
Let me see.

27:04.200 --> 27:05.000
Yeah.

27:05.680 --> 27:06.280
He's dead.

27:06.400 --> 27:07.160
What happened?

27:07.160 --> 27:07.640
Who is it?

27:07.640 --> 27:08.900
What's going on there?

27:09.350 --> 27:10.070
Well...

27:10.090 --> 27:11.720
Wasn't he a physician
from Chongling Valley?

27:11.720 --> 27:12.510
What physician?

27:12.510 --> 27:13.590
He was just a scammer.

27:13.590 --> 27:14.240
A scammer?

27:14.550 --> 27:16.230
He got killed just for cheating someone
out of a bit of money?

27:16.230 --> 27:16.920
Fair point.

27:17.330 --> 27:18.610
Maybe he accidentally

27:18.640 --> 27:19.960
fell into the river and drowned.

27:19.960 --> 27:20.550
Looks more like he was killed.

27:20.550 --> 27:21.350
He probably drowned.

27:21.350 --> 27:22.660
I didn't earn the title
"White Streak in the Waves"

27:22.660 --> 27:23.530
for nothing.

27:24.070 --> 27:25.570
No matter who falls into the water,

27:25.570 --> 27:26.660
I can fish them out.

27:27.830 --> 27:29.030
He drowned on his own.

27:31.110 --> 27:32.070
This is not a Gongshan Jade Tablet.

27:32.070 --> 27:33.160
How is it not?

27:33.480 --> 27:35.350
The material is the same, isn't it?

27:35.350 --> 27:36.400
Besides, everyone knows

27:36.400 --> 27:37.550
you have one.

27:37.920 --> 27:38.920
Even though you show up with the fake one,

27:38.920 --> 27:40.450
no one will suspect a thing.

27:41.000 --> 27:42.730
It's not as simple as you think.

27:43.000 --> 27:44.440
You've been wandering around
Chongling Valley all this time.

27:44.440 --> 27:45.600
You should know

27:45.680 --> 27:46.750
that people have died over this.

27:46.750 --> 27:47.610
You're a mortal

27:47.780 --> 27:48.590
without any cultivation,

27:48.590 --> 27:49.830
yet you carry something of great value.

27:49.830 --> 27:51.480
It's bound to attract covetous eyes
lurking in the shadows.

27:51.480 --> 27:52.510
Be careful, or you might

27:52.510 --> 27:54.970
lose your life
instead of gaining any money.

28:24.350 --> 28:26.010
You certainly took your time.

28:26.590 --> 28:28.270
Acting like you own the place.

28:34.510 --> 28:35.110
What?

28:35.830 --> 28:37.690
You killed someone so ruthlessly

28:38.700 --> 28:39.880
and couldn't even be bothered to

28:39.880 --> 28:41.010
dispose of the body?

28:41.200 --> 28:42.770
[Cang Fengzi, Tianyuan Sect]

28:41.450 --> 28:42.590
Now you come here non-stop,

28:42.590 --> 28:44.440
stealing right under my nose.

28:45.310 --> 28:47.030
Your sect truly is rotten

28:47.270 --> 28:48.470
through and through—

28:48.680 --> 28:50.310
none of you are clean.

28:55.350 --> 28:56.270
I don't have

28:56.750 --> 28:57.810
your jade tablets.

28:57.920 --> 28:59.050
You don't have them?

29:00.350 --> 29:01.110
Before,

29:01.690 --> 29:02.680
I thought you were just

29:02.680 --> 29:04.550
a despicable, shameless scoundrel.

29:04.550 --> 29:06.210
Turns out you're a coward too—

29:06.400 --> 29:07.960
bold enough to act,
but not to own up to it.

29:07.960 --> 29:08.690
That's fine.

29:09.440 --> 29:11.170
I'll find out once I search you.

29:17.880 --> 29:18.400
I

29:18.920 --> 29:20.120
won't repeat myself.

29:20.400 --> 29:21.680
So there's no rule

29:22.790 --> 29:24.160
against stealing here?

29:25.480 --> 29:26.080
Oh, right.

29:28.920 --> 29:29.920
Where is Su Taiyi?

29:30.440 --> 29:31.920
He didn't show up last time,

29:31.920 --> 29:33.580
and now he's not coming at all?

29:34.550 --> 29:35.160
I lost my jade tablets

29:35.160 --> 29:36.620
in your Chongling Valley,

29:37.400 --> 29:39.530
yet everyone present remains silent.

29:40.160 --> 29:43.270
You should at least offer me compensation,
don't you think?

29:43.270 --> 29:44.680
Thirty Immortality Pills

29:44.680 --> 29:46.440
for thirty Gongshan Jade Tablets—

29:46.440 --> 29:47.440
not one pill more.

29:48.400 --> 29:49.070
Besides,

29:49.790 --> 29:51.550
we're only responsible for
researching medicines and refining pills—

29:51.550 --> 29:52.680
nothing beyond that.

29:52.680 --> 29:53.680
That was the rule

29:54.550 --> 29:56.070
you all set back then.

29:58.110 --> 29:59.590
You certainly have

29:59.900 --> 30:01.440
a sharp memory for minor matters.

30:01.440 --> 30:03.570
Young Sect Master Lin, don't be angry.

30:03.590 --> 30:05.270
Even though you won't get anything
from this batch,

30:05.270 --> 30:07.330
there will be some for you in the next.

30:09.880 --> 30:10.940
Easy for you to say.

30:12.000 --> 30:13.790
How about I take this batch,

30:14.240 --> 30:15.840
and you wait for the next one?

30:16.480 --> 30:17.030
You...

30:18.790 --> 30:21.320
Is this conference even going
to start or not?

30:23.880 --> 30:25.350
There are still some who haven't arrived.

30:25.350 --> 30:26.680
But it's time.

30:28.480 --> 30:30.920
Let's count what we have here first.

30:49.030 --> 30:50.000
Lingxu Sect,

30:50.310 --> 30:51.070
two tablets!

30:52.000 --> 30:52.880
Mr. Bai Yun,

30:54.160 --> 30:57.030
only these two tablets are valid.

30:57.980 --> 30:59.110
For the other three,

30:59.220 --> 31:00.830
though made of the same material,

31:00.830 --> 31:02.310
the sizes

31:02.790 --> 31:03.720
don't match.

31:07.110 --> 31:09.790
Dr. Zhu, you really have a sharp eye.

31:10.070 --> 31:10.960
I bought

31:11.030 --> 31:12.750
these three from someone else.

31:12.750 --> 31:13.680
I felt sorry for the seller,

31:13.680 --> 31:14.830
so I bought them.

31:14.870 --> 31:16.590
But I didn't expect him to be a fraud,

31:16.590 --> 31:17.640
selling me fakes.

31:22.920 --> 31:24.180
Daoist Master Gong Yu.

31:25.480 --> 31:26.480
Look carefully.

31:35.000 --> 31:35.930
Sun Moon Cavern,

31:36.440 --> 31:37.160
five!

31:48.720 --> 31:49.920
The Imperial Family,

31:50.350 --> 31:51.110
six!

32:00.270 --> 32:01.530
Lingji Mountain Sect.

32:03.880 --> 32:04.510
None.

32:05.240 --> 32:06.040
My tablets...

32:07.310 --> 32:08.240
Ask him for them.

32:19.070 --> 32:20.160
Tianyuan Sect.

32:24.200 --> 32:24.790
Seven.

32:29.830 --> 32:30.920
Tianyuan Sect,

32:31.240 --> 32:32.150
seven.

32:33.110 --> 32:34.440
Didn't you have 20?

32:35.160 --> 32:36.820
Why are there only seven left?

32:37.000 --> 32:38.480
What happened to the other 13?

32:38.480 --> 32:40.680
Why not bring them out to show everyone?

32:44.960 --> 32:45.550
Senior,

32:46.200 --> 32:47.660
there are already 20 here.

32:51.790 --> 32:52.440
Everyone,

32:53.550 --> 32:56.310
there are now 20 jade tablets in total.

32:57.750 --> 32:59.150
Fellow Cultivator Wang,

32:59.310 --> 33:00.310
where is yours?

33:32.350 --> 33:33.200
Xin Mei?

33:37.480 --> 33:39.030
I'm Xin Mei, a disciple of

33:39.030 --> 33:39.830
Xin Xie Manor.

33:40.200 --> 33:41.400
It's been a long time.

33:41.440 --> 33:43.550
I didn't expect you to
still remember me, Senior.

33:43.550 --> 33:44.960
Are all the ones in your hand

33:44.960 --> 33:46.760
genuine Gongshan Jade Tablets?

33:47.830 --> 33:48.440
Yes.

33:48.830 --> 33:50.560
How did you come to have so many?

33:51.830 --> 33:53.230
If I remember correctly,

33:53.790 --> 33:56.160
your master, Xin Xiong,

33:57.070 --> 33:58.730
only got one tablet back then.

33:58.920 --> 34:00.240
You remember correctly, Senior.

34:00.240 --> 34:01.880
Our sect only had one.

34:03.310 --> 34:04.510
But do all the seniors here

34:04.510 --> 34:06.270
still have the same number
of Gongshan Jade Tablets

34:06.270 --> 34:07.470
they were originally

34:07.880 --> 34:08.920
given?

34:13.590 --> 34:14.840
I, for one, do not.

34:16.670 --> 34:19.000
And there are far fewer people here today.

34:19.030 --> 34:20.630
Senior, why don't you ask them one by one

34:20.630 --> 34:21.550
whether the number of

34:21.550 --> 34:23.110
Gongshan Jade Tablets they have

34:23.110 --> 34:24.760
matches what they were originally given,

34:24.760 --> 34:26.489
and where any extras came from?

34:26.800 --> 34:28.659
Your master is of mediocre skill,

34:28.960 --> 34:30.920
but you have quite the audacity.

34:31.550 --> 34:32.810
Gongshan Jade Tablets

34:33.000 --> 34:34.199
belong to the strong.

34:34.920 --> 34:35.590
Insolent.

34:42.100 --> 34:43.760
You weren't there at the time.

34:44.440 --> 34:45.280
Yet those are

34:45.760 --> 34:48.070
the exact words
your sect's people said to us.

34:48.070 --> 34:49.670
Yet now that it applies to me,

34:49.840 --> 34:51.540
why is it considered insolent

34:51.670 --> 34:52.870
and offensive to you?

34:52.889 --> 34:53.969
Even though you

34:54.000 --> 34:55.710
have those Gongshan Jade Tablets,

34:55.710 --> 34:58.510
you may not
get the Immortality Pills later.

34:58.800 --> 35:00.060
You're right, Senior.

35:04.260 --> 35:05.440
This disciple, Xin Mei,

35:05.440 --> 35:06.950
is a cultivator of Xin Xie Manor.

35:06.950 --> 35:07.960
My master, Xin Xiong,

35:07.960 --> 35:09.550
is a cultivator
of the Great Completion Stage,

35:09.550 --> 35:10.810
now over 200 years old.

35:11.480 --> 35:12.510
I originally came here

35:12.510 --> 35:13.590
with a Gongshan Jade Tablet

35:13.590 --> 35:14.590
to exchange it for

35:15.000 --> 35:16.630
an Immortality Pill for my master.

35:16.630 --> 35:18.360
But my master has no wish to live forever

35:18.360 --> 35:19.550
and has repeatedly advised me

35:19.550 --> 35:20.230
not to come.

35:21.630 --> 35:23.360
At first, I didn't understand.

35:23.720 --> 35:24.480
But after staying here

35:24.480 --> 35:25.630
for a while,

35:25.960 --> 35:27.290
I suddenly realized it.

35:28.150 --> 35:28.880
So I don't

35:28.880 --> 35:29.960
want a single one of

35:30.590 --> 35:32.720
these Gongshan Jade Tablets anymore!

35:35.550 --> 35:36.210
Junior Xin,

35:36.400 --> 35:38.050
my jade tablets have been stolen.

35:38.050 --> 35:38.920
If you don't want yours,

35:38.920 --> 35:40.030
you can sell them to me.

35:40.030 --> 35:41.710
I'll pay whatever price you ask.

35:41.710 --> 35:42.760
Senior Lin,

35:43.150 --> 35:45.280
you want these Gongshan Jade Tablets?

35:45.320 --> 35:46.150
Junior Xin,

35:46.480 --> 35:47.480
Junior Xin.

35:48.200 --> 35:49.680
Our sect also has seniors

35:49.710 --> 35:51.030
nearing the end of their lifespans.

35:51.030 --> 35:53.090
If you don't need these jade tablets,

35:53.150 --> 35:53.960
could you

35:54.190 --> 35:55.360
spare a few for me?

35:55.670 --> 35:56.670
You want some too?

35:57.880 --> 35:58.920
And me.

36:00.800 --> 36:02.060
I was robbed recently,

36:02.880 --> 36:04.740
and my only jade tablet was taken.

36:04.840 --> 36:05.960
Miss, if you are willing

36:05.960 --> 36:07.960
to part with one or two jade tablets,

36:08.760 --> 36:10.160
the Wang family of Jinqiu

36:10.230 --> 36:10.880
will definitely not forget

36:10.880 --> 36:12.680
the great kindness of your sect.

36:17.150 --> 36:18.610
All of you seniors present

36:19.150 --> 36:19.750
are either

36:20.070 --> 36:22.480
accomplished masters
in the cultivation world

36:22.480 --> 36:22.920
or

36:23.360 --> 36:25.360
promising imperial officials.

36:26.150 --> 36:27.630
You are people of great stature

36:27.630 --> 36:29.960
who have seen much and accomplished much.

36:30.110 --> 36:30.670
As for me,

36:31.280 --> 36:32.670
I'm not particularly talented.

36:32.670 --> 36:34.110
After years of cultivation,

36:34.110 --> 36:36.040
I still cannot steady my Dao heart.

36:36.320 --> 36:37.590
Three times I have advanced to
the Golden Core Stage,

36:37.590 --> 36:39.280
and three times I have fallen back.

36:39.280 --> 36:40.440
To this day, I remain nothing more than

36:40.440 --> 36:42.110
a Foundation Establishment cultivator.

36:42.110 --> 36:43.030
Junior Xin,

36:43.150 --> 36:44.550
you're being too modest.

36:44.960 --> 36:46.960
My master said my repeated setbacks

36:46.960 --> 36:48.220
and unstable Dao heart

36:48.230 --> 36:48.960
are due to

36:48.980 --> 36:50.800
a question
that has long lingered in my heart

36:50.800 --> 36:51.860
without an answer.

36:52.280 --> 36:53.510
So I came here this time

36:53.510 --> 36:54.590
to seek someone

36:54.880 --> 36:56.540
who could give me that answer.

36:56.550 --> 36:58.950
If anyone can resolve
the doubt in my heart,

36:59.150 --> 37:01.030
I will naturally offer these jade tablets

37:01.030 --> 37:02.150
with both hands!

37:18.360 --> 37:19.400
I may fall short,

37:19.670 --> 37:21.590
but I'm willing to devote everything
I've learned in my life

37:21.590 --> 37:24.230
to answering your question.

37:24.440 --> 37:25.190
Junior Xin,

37:25.760 --> 37:26.550
please ask.

37:29.400 --> 37:30.150
Mr. Bai Yun,

37:31.480 --> 37:33.920
I heard that your sect is
proficient in mathematics,

37:33.920 --> 37:35.320
especially in complex calculations.

37:35.320 --> 37:36.190
I happen to have a

37:36.190 --> 37:37.590
question about numbers.

37:38.110 --> 37:39.190
Go ahead and ask.

37:41.030 --> 37:42.030
When I was a child,

37:42.670 --> 37:44.280
there were neither Immortality Pills

37:44.280 --> 37:45.610
nor an Immortality Tax.

37:45.760 --> 37:46.670
Let me ask this:

37:47.360 --> 37:49.190
a typical family of five—

37:49.630 --> 37:51.440
the husband goes out to work every day,

37:51.440 --> 37:53.040
earning about 100 wen daily.

37:53.110 --> 37:54.070
How much does his wage

37:54.070 --> 37:55.670
amount to in silver per year?

37:55.960 --> 37:57.480
One hundred wen a day—

37:57.800 --> 37:58.920
that's 300 a month.

37:59.480 --> 38:00.810
Twelve months in a year,

38:01.360 --> 38:03.230
and that makes 36,000 wen.

38:03.590 --> 38:06.070
After accounting for rest days
during holidays and festivals,

38:06.070 --> 38:07.190
by year's end,

38:07.590 --> 38:09.720
that's about 30-some taels of silver.

38:10.440 --> 38:11.550
The wife stays at home,

38:11.550 --> 38:13.190
cooking for the whole family,

38:13.190 --> 38:14.510
mending clothes, and weaving—

38:14.510 --> 38:16.040
spending about 40 wen a day.

38:16.360 --> 38:17.670
The children need schooling,

38:17.670 --> 38:19.510
and the elderly person occasionally
needs medication and doctor visits—

38:19.510 --> 38:20.510
averaged out,

38:20.670 --> 38:22.330
that's another 15 wen per day.

38:22.550 --> 38:23.480
So altogether,

38:23.920 --> 38:25.650
how much do they spend in a year?

38:26.800 --> 38:29.190
Fifty-five wen a day,

38:29.630 --> 38:31.800
which makes 19,000 wen a year—

38:32.280 --> 38:34.480
about 20 taels of silver.

38:35.070 --> 38:36.480
That leaves roughly 10 taels remaining.

38:36.480 --> 38:37.150
Exactly.

38:38.000 --> 38:39.590
So, if they want to use those savings

38:39.590 --> 38:40.400
to buy a house

38:40.480 --> 38:41.800
to leave to their descendants,

38:41.800 --> 38:43.530
how many years would that take?

38:44.190 --> 38:46.480
How much is this house worth?

38:46.590 --> 38:47.510
One hundred taels.

38:47.510 --> 38:48.710
Then it's simple.

38:48.960 --> 38:50.840
It would take 10 years.

38:51.480 --> 38:52.760
If times are bad,

38:52.920 --> 38:54.520
with disasters or hardship,

38:54.590 --> 38:56.800
12 or 13 years would still suffice.

38:58.710 --> 39:01.150
And what about
after the Immortality Tax is added?

39:01.150 --> 39:02.400
The Immortality Tax

39:02.710 --> 39:04.150
varies among the people.

39:04.590 --> 39:06.190
Merchants pay the trade tax,

39:06.480 --> 39:08.030
weavers pay the textile tax,

39:08.030 --> 39:10.110
and farmers pay the land tax.

39:10.400 --> 39:11.800
May I ask, Junior Xin—

39:12.150 --> 39:14.010
which group are you referring to?

39:14.800 --> 39:16.800
Let's take ordinary farmers as an example.

39:16.800 --> 39:18.770
The husband still earns 100 wen a day.

39:18.770 --> 39:20.190
But the wife has to start farming

39:20.190 --> 39:21.480
to help support the household,

39:21.480 --> 39:22.810
making over 10 wen a day.

39:23.150 --> 39:25.030
And their children
no longer need schooling,

39:25.030 --> 39:26.670
and the elderly person no longer
sees a doctor.

39:26.670 --> 39:28.190
The family buys no new clothes all year

39:28.190 --> 39:29.510
and only cooks simple meals

39:29.510 --> 39:30.480
to survive.

39:31.000 --> 39:32.850
So, how many years would it take them

39:32.850 --> 39:33.450
to buy

39:33.480 --> 39:34.810
that house I mentioned?

39:35.110 --> 39:36.760
Food costs 30 wen a day,

39:37.110 --> 39:39.230
so that's 10,800 wen a year,

39:39.760 --> 39:41.590
which converts to 10 taels of silver.

39:41.590 --> 39:42.720
The Immortality Tax

39:42.760 --> 39:44.480
consists of a winter tax and a summer tax.

39:44.480 --> 39:46.360
The winter tax takes 30% of the yield,

39:46.360 --> 39:48.150
and the summer tax takes 40%.

39:48.480 --> 39:50.410
After deducting food expenses...

39:51.840 --> 39:52.970
I've calculated it.

39:53.320 --> 39:54.070
About

39:54.440 --> 39:56.190
1,380 years.

39:57.550 --> 40:00.210
One thousand
three hundred and eighty years...

40:00.590 --> 40:01.320
No!

40:01.920 --> 40:03.920
Mortals live no more than 100 years.

40:04.190 --> 40:06.860
What mortal could possibly
live for 1,380 years?

40:06.860 --> 40:07.520
They simply

40:07.530 --> 40:09.330
could never live to see that day!

40:11.070 --> 40:11.890
Junior Xin,

40:11.920 --> 40:12.400
you...

40:19.710 --> 40:22.440
You're just throwing away the tablets
like this?

40:23.070 --> 40:23.730
Senior Lin,

40:24.590 --> 40:27.190
do you still want
these Gongshan Jade Tablets?

40:29.510 --> 40:31.010
I'm not good at calculations,

40:31.010 --> 40:33.440
nor do I know much
about this Immortality Tax.

40:33.440 --> 40:34.710
When I entered the valley,

40:34.710 --> 40:36.170
I saw you outside.

40:36.590 --> 40:38.590
You arrived in a carriage,

40:38.800 --> 40:39.460
didn't you?

40:39.920 --> 40:41.760
The journey from Lingji Mountain is long,

40:41.760 --> 40:43.020
and many of us had come,

40:43.110 --> 40:44.640
so we had to take a carriage.

40:44.960 --> 40:46.000
Senior, you took

40:46.030 --> 40:47.630
the Xudu–Wucheng route to get here.

40:47.630 --> 40:49.490
Did you stop to rest along the way?

40:50.190 --> 40:51.480
It was desolate all the way,

40:51.480 --> 40:52.940
and inns were hard to find.

40:53.110 --> 40:55.040
So we only stopped briefly in Xudu.

40:56.110 --> 40:56.910
How many times

40:57.070 --> 40:59.130
have you traveled that road, Senior?

40:59.280 --> 41:00.360
Xudu is a necessary pass

41:00.360 --> 41:01.670
on the way to Lingji Mountain.

41:01.670 --> 41:03.070
From childhood until now,

41:03.070 --> 41:05.000
I've traveled it countless times.

41:05.030 --> 41:06.560
Then you must know, Senior,

41:06.800 --> 41:08.070
that what I'm about to say

41:08.070 --> 41:09.130
is no fabrication.

41:10.710 --> 41:12.550
I visited Xudu in my early years.

41:13.070 --> 41:15.110
Back then, Xudu was prosperous

41:15.230 --> 41:16.320
and bustling,

41:16.630 --> 41:19.000
with carriages and horses
streaming ceaselessly.

41:19.000 --> 41:21.070
There were hundreds of residential blocks
in the city,

41:21.070 --> 41:23.670
and the official roads outside
branched out in all directions,

41:23.670 --> 41:25.400
reaching as far as North Xiang.

41:25.640 --> 41:26.840
Carriages and cargo ships

41:26.840 --> 41:28.230
ran day and night without cease.

41:28.230 --> 41:30.360
Even miles beyond the official roads,

41:30.400 --> 41:32.360
one could still smell ripening grain

41:32.360 --> 41:34.320
and see the gentle curls of cooking smoke.

41:34.320 --> 41:36.000
Villages lined the outskirts of the city,

41:36.000 --> 41:37.200
stretching on and on.

41:38.760 --> 41:39.620
Does any of that

41:39.800 --> 41:41.710
match what you saw

41:42.030 --> 41:42.590
and heard

41:42.960 --> 41:43.890
on your journey?

41:45.550 --> 41:46.950
What caused this change?

41:48.800 --> 41:50.000
The Immortality Tax.

41:50.550 --> 41:51.750
It's counted by head.

41:52.450 --> 41:53.640
From newborns

41:53.670 --> 41:55.200
who know nothing but crying

41:55.290 --> 41:56.440
to the elderly too frail and bleary-eyed

41:56.440 --> 41:57.770
to care for themselves,

41:58.400 --> 41:59.400
no one was exempt.

42:00.260 --> 42:01.150
To evade the tax,

42:01.150 --> 42:02.110
many families

42:02.710 --> 42:04.800
stopped marrying and having children.

42:04.800 --> 42:05.880
The elderly, unwilling to burden

42:05.880 --> 42:06.810
their families,

42:07.110 --> 42:09.440
took poison to end their lives
one after another.

42:09.440 --> 42:11.640
Others abandoned
their homes and livelihoods,

42:11.640 --> 42:12.960
choosing to become refugees

42:12.960 --> 42:14.400
just to survive!

42:15.590 --> 42:16.550
As a result,

42:17.030 --> 42:18.710
not even one in ten villages along the way

42:18.710 --> 42:19.880
survived.

42:21.400 --> 42:22.000
Indeed.

42:23.000 --> 42:24.360
Back then, the War Demons,

42:24.360 --> 42:26.480
in order to repair the heavenly ladder,

42:26.480 --> 42:28.440
planted the sacred seed
of the divine tree,

42:28.440 --> 42:31.440
vainly attempting to sacrifice half of
all living beings in the mortal world

42:31.440 --> 42:32.840
to awaken it.

42:33.360 --> 42:34.880
When the humans learned of this,

42:34.880 --> 42:36.010
they rose in revolt,

42:36.280 --> 42:37.960
launching thousands of wars

42:38.230 --> 42:40.290
that left millions dead and wounded.

42:40.400 --> 42:41.150
Even so,

42:41.760 --> 42:43.560
many villages and ancient towns

42:43.760 --> 42:45.160
still managed to endure.

42:45.480 --> 42:46.740
But strangely enough,

42:46.920 --> 42:48.880
the world has been
at peace in recent years,

42:48.880 --> 42:50.940
yet things are far worse than before.

42:53.510 --> 42:55.030
Must a great war break out

42:55.510 --> 42:57.440
and the Human Race face extinction

42:57.840 --> 42:59.840
before our immortal sects remember

42:59.880 --> 43:00.810
that we were once

43:01.760 --> 43:02.840
ordinary people?
